column2: information that can be used to identify
Personal information means information that can be used to identify and contact you.
This demographic information may be associated with your personal information.

Like many websites, we employ cookies in certain areas of the Site(s) to allow us to provide information which is targeted to your interests and to make your online experience more convenient. For example, when you return to one of our websites after logging in, cookies provide information to the website so that the website will remember who you are.
